videos.description: No. 13 LSU extends its lead to double digits against No. 1 South Carolina as Khayla Pointer finds Alexis Morris on the break for the layup.

videos.description: Aliyah Boston posts 19 points and 17 rebounds as No. 1 South Carolina erases a double-digit deficit to win at No. 13 LSU.

videos.description: No. 1 South Carolina's Dawn Staley credits the gritty 66-60 win over No. 13 LSU to the extra 23 rebounds the Gamecocks grabbed.
videos.headline: Staley says rebounding led to Gamecocks' win over LSU
